      <img src="ladkiyan2.jpg" class="img-fluid  " alt="..." width="692" height="400" style="    box-shadow: 0 10px 16px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 20%), 0 6px 20px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 19%) !important;" >
